OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fnight with rain feeding in from the
OL,7,Fwest, becoming persistent and heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes across northern Argyll. Best of
OL,9,Fany drier spells in the south.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAnother mostly cloudy day.
OL,12,FSome patchy rain, mainly for Argyll
OL,13,Fwhere heavy at first.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,16,Fcloudy, patchy rain on Tuesday, some
OL,17,Fbright spells. Wednesday and Thursday
OL,18,Fwill be mainly dry with sunny spells
OL,19,Fand becoming warm, Argyll possibly
OL,20,Fcloudier at times, patchy rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
